<section class="resume">
  <div class="resume-container">
    <div class="slideshow-container">
      <%= image_tag "AntManPosterisation.jpeg", class: "slide intrigue-slide active" %>
      <div class="intrigue-overlay">
        <h1>Backstage</h1>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="artist-description">
      <p>
Observateur attentif entre ombres et lumières,
je scrute les coins de rues et le vide du ciel.
« Think Quieter, Listen Louder » fut l’un de mes premiers slogans,
une invitation à capter l’invisible et à entendre l’indicible.
      </p>
      <p>
        L’intrigue n’est pas un effet. C’est un regard. Le mien cherche ce que l’on ne veut pas toujours voir.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function () {
    let slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");
    let current = 0;

    function showSlide(index) {
      slides.forEach((slide, i) => {
        slide.classList.remove("active");
      });
      slides[index].classList.add("active");
    }

    function nextSlide() {
      current = (current + 1) % slides.length;
      showSlide(current);
    }

    showSlide(current); // Affiche la première slide
    setInterval(nextSlide, 4000); // Changement toutes les 4 secondes
  });
</script>

<style>
  body {
    font-family: 'Lato';
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }
  h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2rem;
  }
  .resume{
    padding:40px;
    bottom: 10px;
    top:10px;
    width:100%;
    height:auto;
    background-color: black;
    color:black;
  }
.resume-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: stretch;
  gap: 40px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.slideshow-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 45%;
  height: 60vh;
  overflow: hidden;
}

  .slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;       /* Remplit sans déformer */
    object-position: center; /* Centre l'image */
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }
  .slide.active {
    opacity: 1;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .artist-description {
  width: 45%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
}

.artist-description h2 {
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  font-size: 2rem;
  margin-bottom: 16px;
  color: white;
}

.artist-description p {
  font-size: 1rem;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: #ccc;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}
  .gallery-section {
    padding: 40px;
    background: white;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .gallery-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .grid-gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .grid-gallery img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 180px;
    object-fit: cover;
  /*  border-radius: 8px;*/
    box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.2s ease;
  }
  .grid-gallery img:hover {
    transform: scale(1.03);
  }
  .intrigue-slide {
  position: absolute;
  top: 50%;
  left: 70%;
  width: auto;          /* Laisse la largeur automatique */
  height: 100%;         /* Prend toute la hauteur du conteneur */
  max-width: none;      /* Pas de limite max sur la largeur */
  max-height: 100%;     /* Limite la hauteur au conteneur */
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%) scale(1.05); /* Centre + zoom */
  filter: brightness(1.2) contrast(1.1) saturate(2);
  transition: transform 10s ease-in-out;
  object-fit: cover;    /* Pour couvrir sans déformer */
  object-position: center;
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out, transform 10s ease-in-out;
}
}

@keyframes zoom-slow {
  from { transform: scale(1); }
  to { transform: scale(1.1); }
}

.intrigue-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  z-index: 2;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.2));
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  pointer-events: none;
  text-align: center;
}

.intrigue-overlay h1 {
  color: white;
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
  line-height: 1.6;
  padding: 0 1rem;
  max-width: 80%;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
  animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in-out both;
}

.intrigue-overlay h1 span {
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-size: 1.4rem;
}

@keyframes fadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
  to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

</style>
